MBOMBELA &#8211; Sembcorp Silulumanzi cut the water supply to parts of the town this morning.Spokesman Richmond Jele said it appeared that in the course of construction work, a main was hit.The supple had to be turned off while technicians attempted to fix it. Hopefully, if all goes well, supply will be restored soon, he said.Kiepersol and Stinkhout streets were expected have water returned by 12:30, and Piet Retief Street by 14:00.Municipality keeps water restrictions